sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor KH as Khach hang
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant CartDB as Cart DB - MongoDB
    participant OrderDB as Order DB
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant MoMo as MoMo API
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ

    KH->>GW: POST /api/orders/checkout
    Note over KH,GW: paymentMethod=MOMO<br/>orderType, note, discounts, promotions
    GW->>Order: Forward request - yeu cau auth

    Order->>CartDB: findByCustomerId(customerId)
    CartDB-->>Order: cart record

    alt Gio hang trong
        Order-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>KH: Gio hang trong
    else Gio hang co san pham
        Order->>Order: Chuyen cart items sang order items
        Order->>Order: buildOrderDetails - tinh subtotal, discount, promotion
        Note over Order: initialStatus=PENDING_PAYMENT<br/>orderChannel=ONLINE, paymentMethod=MOMO

        Order->>OrderDB: order.create - status=PENDING_PAYMENT
        Note over Order,OrderDB: order_details, order_discounts<br/>order_promotions, status_log
        OrderDB-->>Order: order record

        Order->>Payment: POST /api/payments/initiate
        Note over Order,Payment: orderId, totalAmount<br/>paymentMethod=MOMO, orderCode

        Payment->>MoMo: createMomoPayment - amount, orderInfo

        alt MoMo loi - resultCode != 0
            MoMo-->>Payment: resultCode != 0
            Payment-->>Order: 400 Bad Request
            Order->>MQ: Publish order_exchange / order.created
            Note over Order,MQ: Fallback - Payment Service tu tao CASH payment

        else MoMo thanh cong
            MoMo-->>Payment: payUrl, deeplink, qrCodeUrl
            Payment->>Payment: payment.create - status=PENDING, provider_order_id
            Payment-->>Order: 200 OK - payUrl
        end

        Order->>CartDB: clearCart(cart_id)
        Order-->>GW: 201 Created
        Note over Order,GW: orderId, orderCode<br/>status=PENDING_PAYMENT, payUrl
        GW-->>KH: Don hang da tao - chuyen den trang MoMo
    end

    Note over KH,MQ: KH thanh toan tren MoMo<br/>MoMo gui IPN callback - xem diagram 16

